# Treat this project as standalone, not part of any pnpm workspace found in ancestor dirs.
# /home/dfy has a pnpm-workspace.yaml that would otherwise make pnpm hoist shared deps
# to the root and incorrectly report "Already up to date" while leaving node_modules empty.
# Note: pnpm 11 reads `--ignore-workspace` from CLI only; this file alone is not enough.
# Run installs as:  pnpm install --ignore-workspace
